          "reviewBody": "I had the privilege of being a part of Nehru World School, and I must say it was an exceptional experience. The dedicated faculty went above and beyond to provide a nurturing learning environment. The curriculum was thoughtfully designed, offering a perfect blend of academics and extracurricular activities. The school's emphasis on holistic development helped me grow not only academically but also as an individual. The facilities were top-notch, creating an inspiring atmosphere for learning. Moreover, the strong sense of community fostered lifelong friendships. The school truly exceeded my expectations, and I highly recommend it for anyone seeking an enriching educational journey.\nI still miss Virtual World Tour !",
